      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 30 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 30 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>離，利貞，亨。畜牝牛，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Li indicates that, (in regard to what it denotes), it will be advantageous to be firm and correct, and that thus there will be free course and success. Let (its subject) also nourish (a docility like that of) the cow, and there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
