      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 30 九三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 30 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：日昃之離，不鼓缶而歌，則大耋之嗟，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows its subject in a position like that of the declining sun. Instead of playing on his instrument of earthenware, and singing to it, he utters the groans of an old man of eighty. There will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
