      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 30 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 30 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：突如其來如，焚如，死如，棄如。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows the manner of its subject's coming. How abrupt it is, as with fire, with death, to be rejected (by all)!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
