      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 30 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：出涕沱若，戚嗟若，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows its subject as one with tears flowing in torrents, and groaning in sorrow. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
