      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 30 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 30 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九：王用出征，有嘉折首，獲其匪丑，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost NINE, undivided, shows the king employing its subject in his punitive expeditions. Achieving admirable (merit), he breaks (only) the chiefs (of the rebels). Where his prisoners were not their associates, he does not punish. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
